                        "ancestorRefs": [],
                        "body": "<div class=\"u-mt-4\"><div class=\"u-mt-3 u-font-bold u-mb-3\">User notes:</div><div class=\"u-mt-3 u-italic u-mb-3\"><span class=\"u-font-bold\">About this chapter: </span>Chapter 12 supplements <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/washington/wa-residential-code-2021/chapter/1/scope-and-administration#1\">Chapter 1</a> and establishes the scope of coverage for Chapters <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/washington/wa-residential-code-2021/chapter/13/general-mechanical-system-requirements#13\">13</a> through <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/washington/wa-residential-code-2021/chapter/24/fuel-gas#24\">24</a>. The applicability of code provisions to existing <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/washington/wa-residential-code-2021/chapter/2/definitions#mechanical_system\">mechanical systems</a> and <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/washington/wa-residential-code-2021/chapter/24/fuel-gas#appliance\">appliances</a> is established herein.</div><div class=\"u-mt-3 u-italic u-mb-3\"><span class=\"u-font-bold\">Code development reminder:</span> Code change proposals to this chapter will be considered by the IRC\u2014<a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/washington/wa-residential-code-2021/chapter/2/definitions#plumbing\">Plumbing</a>/<a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/washington/wa-mechanical-code-2018\">Mechanical Code</a> Development Committee during the 2021 (Group A) Code Development Cycle.</div></div>",
